Package: maskpii
Type: Package
Title: Mask Personally Identifiable Information
Version: 0.2.0
Authors@R: c(
  person("Finite Field, K.K.", email = "dev@finitefield.org", role = c("aut", "cre"))
)
Description: Lightweight utilities for masking personally identifiable information
  such as email addresses and phone numbers. The masking logic is consistent across
  language implementations and avoids regular expressions for predictable behavior.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
URL: https://finitefield.org/en/oss/mask-pii
BugReports: https://github.com/finitefield-org/mask-pii/issues
Encoding: UTF-8
Suggests: testthat (>= 3.0.0)
Keywords: pii, masking, email, phone, privacy
